<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id122c81b5-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777" identifier="/us/usc/t44/s1511"><num value="1511">§ 1511.</num><heading> International agreements excluded from provisions of chapter</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter does not apply to treaties, conventions, protocols, and other international agreements, or proclamations thereof by the President.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id122c81b6-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/620">Pub. L. 90–620</ref>, <date date="1968-10-22">Oct. 22, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/1278">82 Stat. 1278</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
