<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="id122c81b8-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on 44 U.S. Code, 1964 ed., § 312 (<ref href="/us/act/1935-07-26/ch417/s12">July 26, 1935, ch. 417, § 12</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/49/503">49 Stat. 503</ref>).</p>
</note>
